messages.message:
Hi Team,
Recently, we encountered issue with Victoriametrics crashing in certain environments. I’ve compiled a comprehensive write-up detailing the issue, along with the actions we’ve taken to address it. You can access the document by clicking here (https://docs.google.com/document/d/1xensB6EQUo9Z-1Q6EwG30MhNCopNGnUz3nqTBjiff14). If you encounter any difficulties with Victoriametrics, we recommend updating to the latest version of either a major release or the master branch for a potential resolution.
c.c. @sudeep @shaunak @HH
